# Session [20] – Network+

## Main Topics
- Dynamic Routing chist?  
- Tarze kar dynamic routing  
- Estefadeh-ha dar network  

## Flashback – Dynamic Routing Basics
- Dynamic Routing = router ha **khodkar** masir ha ra yad migirand va update mikonand  
- Routers az protocol haye routing estefade mikonand (mesl RIP, OSPF, EIGRP)  

## Explanation

### Tarze Kar
- Routers data ro exchange mikonand ta **routing table** ro update konand  
- Masir ha bar asas metrics (distance, cost, speed) entekhab mishavand  
- Routers be sorat automatic masir ha ra adjust mikonand vaghti network taghir mikonad  

### Estefadeh-ha
- Networks bozorg va complex  
- Traffic dynamic va unpredictable  
- Efficient va fault-tolerant  

### Example
| Protocol | Metric | Update Type | Use Case |
|----------|--------|-------------|----------|
| RIP      | Hop Count | Periodic   | Small to medium networks |
| OSPF     | Cost      | Triggered  | Medium to large networks |
| EIGRP    | Composite | Triggered  | Enterprise networks |

